ji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最尾睇唔開咪自殺囉"},{"pid":"31827c2c70d33a084eb95b21c0746e97bfdbbe8f","tid":907514,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T01:45:51.000Z","msg":"煩膠中二病"},{"pid":"ab571cddf55962fd7ddbb977baf1bb0eeefeda4b","tid":907514,"uid":118186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T01:51:17.000Z","msg":"多愁善感 好多野諗<br />\n但語言表達唔到 唯有創作<br />\n覺得好孤獨因為活係自己既世界<br />\n最後被孤獨呑噬"},{"pid":"22e3b873bc6e5d62a94bb0274932e33a7c07d5b5","tid":907514,"uid":179275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T02:43:30.000Z","msg":"藝術家可以做開心既作品<br />\n唔一定要係負能量既野<br />\n呢d係中國香港社會俾藝術家既定型<br />\n<br />\n點睇成日要自殺? 因為窮囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"105489c79e5ececdb9f6f05236204ddba5ce006b","tid":907514,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22e3b873bc6e5d62a94bb0274932e33a7c07d5b5","tid":907514,"uid":179275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T02:43:30.000Z","msg":"藝術家可以做開心既作品<br />\n唔一定要係負能量既野<br />\n呢d係中國香港社會俾藝術家既定型<br />\n<br />\n點睇成日要自殺? 因為窮囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T02:46:58.000Z","msg":"事實上好多偉大作品都同悲觀有關<br />\n<br />\n應該多過開心作品"},{"pid":"a03d6bf176ce054bbc15ded0a3633b0d869fe638","tid":907514,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T02:48:16.000Z","msg":"調返轉諗你 你個人咁開心 喺現實咁滿足, 你就未必會擺咁多心機喺藝術作品到"},{"pid":"ccae9c6e3830c7233cde9b73fa086d9e070851dc","tid":907514,"uid":137220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a03d6bf176ce054bbc15ded0a3633b0d869fe638","tid":907514,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T02:48:16.000Z","msg":"調返轉諗你 你個人咁開心 喺現實咁滿足, 你就未必會擺咁多心機喺藝術作品到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T02:49:02.000Z","msg":"因為你喺現實咁開心，你就會去追求現實上令你開心嘅嘢， 而唔係擺精神喺藝術度"},{"pid":"6c80d34a831baf98f0e364e957698bb40b3d0577","tid":907514,"uid":66436,"like":0,"dislike